      "date": "2013-04-05 18:23:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nSince it failed maloo, I looked at this again.  I flip-flopped and removed EXPORT_SYMBOL.  Since linkea_entry_pack is not delared in lustre_linkea.h, it probably doesn't make sense to leave it exported.  And I don't want to add it to the header.",
